ccessful investment businesses mr cogut founded pegasus capital in  and serves as its chairman and president in  mr cogut cofounded and was one of the original partners at apollo advisors lp a position he held for five years preceding the creation of pegasus capital mr cogut is an active philanthropist in the fields of improving education building civil society and championing environmental and health issues mr cogut serves as chairman of the polyphony foundation an organi  read more craig cogut joined the board on december   and was appointed chairman of the board on february   mr cogut has spent a career building successful investment businesses mr cogut founded pegasus capital in  and serves as its chairman and president in  mr cogut cofounded and was one of the original partners at apollo advisors lp a position he held for five years preceding the creation of pegasus capital mr cogut is an active philanthropist in the fields of improving education building civil society and championing environmental and health issues mr cogut serves as chairman of the polyphony foundation an organization that he cofounded to provide equal opportunity music education for arab and jewish israeli youth in addition mr cogut serves as a trustee of brown university and board member for arizona state universitys global institute of sustainability for human rights first for the mccain institute for international leadership at arizona state university and for the r regions of climate action mr cogut is a member of the executive council of the clinton health access initiative and serves as the chairman of the cogut center for the humanities at brown university mr cogut is an alumnus of brown university and harvard law school pegasus capital intends to elect mr cogut to serve as a director pursuant to its rights set forth in the series i certificate of designation and described elsewhere in this proxy statement we believe mr cogut is qualified to serve on the board because of his significant experience in global manufacturing and extensive experience in business finance and investing source lighting science group corporation on      sign up for equilar atlas and view craig m coguts full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like craig m cogut more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in craig m coguts network and community follow changes in craig m coguts employment and moneyinmotion connect with craig m cogut through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example craig m cogut craig m coguts connections  sign up now to view craig m coguts  connections » adam m aron dir chief executive officer and president amc entertainment holdings inc frank j biondi board member seagate technology plc charles m davis former board member boingo wireless inc debra l lee board member wgl holdings inc richard a friedman board member hyatt hotels corporation karel r den daas board member valmont industries inc f philip handy board member anixter international inc brian t moynihan president chief executive officer and chairman of the board bank of america corporation ruth j simmons board member square inc stephen c hilbert former chairman and chief executive officer cno financial group inc popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch executive chairman te connectivity ltd john j kita evp and cfo a o smith elon r musk ceo and chairman tesla daniel a dematteo executive chairman gamestop corp david j oconnor president and ceo the madison square garden company × claim your profile coming soon interested in updating your biography and work history were working on making it happen well email you when this feature is available please enter valid email address done thank you for your interest ok browse executive profiles  a  b  c  d  e  f  g  h  i  j  k  l  m  n  o  p  q  r  s  t  u  v  w  x  y  z e